user.biography:
Official account of New Glarus Brewing Co. Thanks for checking us out. We think you're pretty great too.
Employee Owned. Only in Wisconsin.
Cheers!

node.text: Let’s have some fun, where were you when you had your first New Glarus brew and what beer did you choose? 🍺 #onlyinwisconsin #buylocal #memorylane

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by New Glarus Brewing Company on July 16, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Want to be a part of the decision-making for the 2022 New Glarus brewing schedule? Go to our website and pick up to 5 of your favorite New Glarus brews by simply clicking ‘Vote’ next to the beers of your choice. Voting ends July 31st! Cheers!

node.text: Take me out to the ball game, Take me out with the crowd; Buy me some peanuts and a spotted cow, I don’t care if I never get back. ⚾️🐄 #drink #buylocal

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by New Glarus Brewing Company on June 25, 2021.

node.text: New Glarus Brewing Company proudly announces Lots O' Peach 21. This Peach Sour Brown brings to mind chin dripping goodness of sun-soaked peaches. Our Wild Fruit Cave delight sparkles with sour brown ale juiciness balanced by just the right amount of funky stone fruit pit center. Ripe summer peach notes bounce a greeting to your nose before overwhelming your senses with lush memories evoked of summer’s ripe fruit decadence. It has begun shipping and if it isn't in your favorite retail establishment yet, we hope it will soon! Cheers!
